  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms </strong>are around 25m² and sleep two people. </p>
<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms</strong> are more spacious at around 28m<span>² and sleep two people. </span></p>
<p><strong>Premium Twin Rooms</strong> are round 35m<span>² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed).</span></p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are the hotel's largest rooms at around 40m<span>² and comfortably sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed).</span></p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are around 20m<span>².</span></p>
<p>All rooms are comfortably furnished in either a classic style with carpets or alpine style with wooden floors. Rooms are twin beds but please specify at time of booking if you would like the beds made up as a double. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
